### If in doubt, quote the application name. Otherwise, consult this list for supported formats:
## GOOD::	notepad.exe
## GOOD::	notepad.exe C:\Users\myname\Documents\perlscript.pl
## BAD::	notepad.exe "C:\Users\myname\Documents\perlscript.pl"
## BAD::	notepad.exe "C:\Users\myname\Documents\Folder Name\perlscript.pl"
## GOOD::	"notepad.exe" "C:\Users\myname\Documents\Folder Name\perlscript.pl"
## BAD::	C:\Path With Space\file.exe
## BAD::	C:\Path With Space\file.exe C:\somefile_for_arg
## GOOD::	"C:\Path With Space\file.exe"
## GOOD::	"C:\Path With Space\file.exe" C:\somefile_for_arg
## GOOD::	"C:\Path With Space\file.exe" "C:\somefile_for_arg"

